The paper focuses on using Deep Convolutional Neural Networks for image understanding and sentiment analysis, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of transfer learning also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the datasets used in the experiments are from social media platforms, indicating a possible relevance to information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
